Discover what's possible

Capture participant touchpoints and status updates using Coordinator Surveys

Coordinator Surveys let you log contact notes, visits, participant status, and other additional information directly within each participant's record. Use captured information to power automated workflows or update segments across your project.

Build surveys that coordinators can complete to do the following:

  • Log calls, notes, clinic visits, and surgery dates
  • Contact participants and logging information
  • Document withdrawal reason
  • Update participant status
